Definition: the speech act of answering an attack on your assertions
Example: his refutation of the charges was short and persuasive; in defense he said the other man started it
Synonyms: verb, communication, refute, defense, defence, answer, the, speech, act, of, answering, an, attack, on, your, assertions, his, charges, was, short, and, persuasive, in, he, said, other, man, started, it
Category: noun.communication
